{"tid":788970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(想節能)  不敵貿易戰  中國輪胎大廠永泰申請破產","createTime":"2018-08-22T01:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T01:04:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7208a42a8c5982e85753cf8b285b0c1d62aba217","tid":788970,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KSkg9TzfM55aHAHRdLjbHQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzQwO2g9MjI3O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/324433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKSkg9TzfM55aHAHRdLjbHQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzQwO2g9MjI3O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F324433.jpg&h=57fab62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">受貿易戰影響，中國輪胎行業持續洗牌。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】中美貿易戰加徵關稅不斷，企業先遭殃。繼黃豆進口商山東晨曦集團申請破產後，中國輪胎大廠山東永泰集團也申請破產。中國最高人民法院諮詢委員會副主任杜萬華警告，中美貿易戰升級可能發生企業破產潮，人民法院應當及早研判以防不測。<br />\n<br />\n永泰集團成立於一九九六年，輪胎產品主要銷往歐美市場。鼎盛時期，員工逾五千人，年生產全鋼載重子午線輪胎一百五十萬套，曾列為全球輪胎行業七十五強，二〇一六年入選中國化工企業七十強。可惜，在本月二日，山東省東營市中級人民法院發布永泰集團破產清算報告，正式啟動該公司的破產清算程序。<br />\n<br />\n永泰集團之死，除了中國輪胎業產能嚴重過剩外，也離不開歐美長期打壓中國輪胎進口。美國自二〇〇七年起，便對中國輪胎發起反傾銷與反補貼的「雙反」調查，加徵「雙反」關稅。貿易戰七月開打後，美國加徵三百四十億美元中國產品兩成五關稅，涉及航空輪胎產品。隨後更公布擬加徵兩千億中國商品關稅，囊括所有中國輸美輪胎品種。中國化工報表示，中國是全球輪胎生產和出口大國，去年中國便生產輪胎九億條。<br />\n<br />\n面對貿易戰規模擴大，涵蓋美國愈來愈多的日常用品和原料，美國企業也多感憂慮。美國政府周一（二十日）就加徵兩千億美元中國產品關稅，舉行為期六天的聽證會。多數企業代表以「不可修復」形容關稅帶來的損失，還有企業指將會大量裁員，以降低關稅增加的成本。另一邊廂，最高人民法院諮詢委員會副主任杜萬華上月撰文，也擔憂貿易戰關稅規模擴大，則導致愈多「在華企業會陸續陷入破產困境。」故此，他呼籲法院應當及行研判目前形勢，甚至應考慮建立審判破產審的平台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BC%AA%E8%83%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%A0%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%B0%E7%94%B3%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2-221117425.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E8%2583%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%2594%25A2-221117425.html&d=Bww1wnCBjfkroq22lFLcxACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b1411ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BC%AA%E8%83%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%A0%E6%B0%B8%E6%B3%B0%E7%94%B3%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2-221117425.html</a>"},{"pid":"99fdfb8ac797ca29e8c3824bec3e1b25dfedd75e","tid":788970,"uid":144626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"而家唔方唔節能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb4e959aab32857b1a43f6fb40f159566a5640e","tid":788970,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n破產+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8789c0e156a1ac15177046ddba1be56e5f67f3c3","tid":788970,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"撚太撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bcd60cb10e34496dcee3d586c66225292170e8","tid":788970,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:03:27.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"5551753362c42456346a5f234eb3099c308ec19c","tid":788970,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8789c0e156a1ac15177046ddba1be56e5f67f3c3","tid":788970,"uid":51057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"撚太撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c4b13be81f55285765acfec31d90ef5a8edb04","tid":788970,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:53:13